1. *Tomas* je juče bio na žurki. (*Tomas* was at the party yesterday.)
2. Da li si video *Tomasa*? (*Have you seen* Tomas*?*)
3. *Tomasa* čeka njegova devojka. (*Tomas's* girlfriend is waiting for him.)
4. Kada je *Tomas* stigao? (*When did* Tomas *arrive?*)
5. *Tomasu* je bilo dosadno na sastanku. (*Tomas* was bored at the meeting.)
6. *Tomase*, reci nam šta misliš o tome. (*Tomas*, tell us what you think about it.)
7. Svi su voleli da se druže sa *Tomasom*. (*Everyone liked to hang out with* Tomas.)
8. *Tomasa* su pozvali da govori na konferenciji. (*Tomas* was invited to speak at the conference.)
9. *Tomasove* cipele su stare i poderane. (*Tomas's* shoes are old and worn out.)
10. *Tomasa* neće biti na poslu sledeća dva dana. (*Tomas* won't be at work for the next two days.)